    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Replica in wax obtained from the reusable mold of an original model. Inter-models are used in indirect lost-wax casting. Inter-models are often slush molded. One inter-model may vary from another through additions or changes made in the wax before the investment is applied.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
